Cap Gemini May Announce a Takeover by Year’s End, Investir Says

-- B y   T a r a   P a t e l
-- 
2011-07-30T11:19:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-30/cap-gemini-may-announce-a-takeover-by-year-s-end-investir-says.html
Cap Gemini SA (CAP)  Chief Executive
Officer Paul Hermelin said the computer-services company may
announce one or two acquisitions before the end of the year,
 Investir  reported, citing an interview.  Cap Gemini will pursue a strategy of “very targeted”
asset purchases, Hermelin was quoted as saying. The company has
carried out seven transactions so far this year, according to
the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tara Patel in Paris at   tpatel2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Will Kennedy at   wkennedy3@bloomberg.net  